(18, 158, 'Simpli Features', 'simpli-features', '', 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 1, 0, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"author\":\"\",\"robots\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '', '', 29, 30, 1, 'simpli-features', 'com_content', 'JoomlArt is excited to announce that we are going to release JA Simpli this April (planned on Mid of April). Simpli is truly Free Joomla template and probably will be the best free Joomla templates as other templates in our Free Joomla template series: T3 Blank, Purity I, Purity II and Purity III. JA Simpli is clean and light without any framework, it is fast, responsive ande easy to customize based on well strutured codebase and intuitive admin panel.', -2, '{\"category_layout\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"image_alt\":\"\"}', 42, '2019-10-21 06:15:43', 42, '2019-10-21 06:15:43'),
